Margaret Vyner https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margaret_Vyner 0 Margaret Leila Vyner (3 December 1914 in Armidale, New South Wales – 30 October 1993 in Reading, England) was an Australian-born model and actress who appeared in British films. She collaborated with husband Hugh Williams on a number of successful theatre projects in the 1950s and 60s.
